{"tid":1693135,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"千人示威堵路 跳閘衝進地鐵高喊「反警察」口號","createTime":"2019-11-04T12:17:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-04T12:56:15.000Z","uid":184679,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"2eea24ade0d44c846d24c5472c0ba4ea039e1f0e","tid":1693135,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T12:17:54.000Z","msg":"美國紐約1日爆發民眾示威，為抗議警察濫用暴力，及增加警力巡邏防逃票者而走上街頭，還有示威者穿過地鐵驗票閘逃票入站，高喊反警察口號。<br />\n<br />\n綜合外媒報導，導火線為近日發生的警察濫用暴力事件，及當局打算增加地鐵巡警人力以防逃票。整起示威歷經2個小時，他們走上布魯克林街頭，包圍交通運輸管理局的巴士，在車身上塗鴉反警標語。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/news/600/2019/11/04/phpUNON1P.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2Fnews%2F600%2F2019%2F11%2F04%2FphpUNON1P.jpg&h=02b3ae7f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n（圖擷自Taylor Lorenz推特）<br />\n<br />\n大批示威者對「地鐵票價及警察」怨恨氣氛濃厚，高舉「免費交通」、「去你的2.75美元票價」等訴求，還有人喊「紐約警局（NYPD）你們知道種族主義者這個詞怎麼拼嗎」、「逮捕付不起2.75美元車費的人，不會讓任何人更安全，是在破壞社會」。<br />\n<br />\n有群示威者站在地鐵門口，喊著「別碰黑人孩子」、「別讓這些豬碰我們」等訴求，甚至有人越過地鐵閘門，逃票衝入站內表達抗議。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/news/600/2019/11/04/phpUrJ6Zr.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2Fnews%2F600%2F2019%2F11%2F04%2FphpUrJ6Zr.jpg&h=e23cc686&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n（圖擷自Taylor Lorenz推特）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2966509\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2966509&d=giu1nYcgFqEI960N5jmVcSgGTjEty4RfxMaQWzCDCUQ%3D&h=8c154822\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2966509&h=22446153\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2966509</a>"},{"pid":"e589ead5c9efb26f20e093668c9977c8dc050555","tid":1693135,"uid":24306,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T12:19:04.000Z","msg":"失民心了"},{"pid":"ae5939fe035786141b0a9dee2bf217de7c91e376","tid